Author: eefredd
Text: But like look on the positive side,  You’re healthy and she’s possibly still underweight. Being skinny while pregnant isn’t really a good thing, babies need lots of nutrients to grow etc.

Author: LawrenAnne4
Text: Literally feel like you’re reading my mind rn. I’m instagram friends with a girl I was close with in middle school who really kickstarted my restricting habits and I see her posting these bodycheck selfies weekly and I can’t believe there was a time when I was thinner than her and I let that slip away.
